description:
Bankruptcy and other financial issues affect many people in Kennewick, Washington, and throughout the Tri-County area. At the law offices of Olsen Daines Bankruptcy Attorneys, we understand the stress and difficulties that often come with these struggles. With over 30 years of experience, we have dedicated our practice to helping those who need assistance through the bankruptcy process as well as help rebuilding their credit, avoiding car repossession, stopping license suspension, paying off back child support and seeking solace from creditor harassment.

During a free initial consultation, clients meet with a compassionate attorney and discuss the circumstances surrounding their situation. The legal team at our client-centered law offices will answer questions and explore all legal options available. We leave no stone unturned when it comes to uncovering the best route of action for our clients. Furthermore, we gladly accept credit cards as a form of payment for our services.

The law offices of Olsen Daines Bankruptcy Attorneys also assist people across Oregon in personal injury cases involving truck collisions, car accidents, birth injuries, wrongful death, pedestrian accidents and traumatic brain damage. Getting back on track following a catastrophic accident may be challenging, and our attorneys stand by our clients every step of the way.

Our legal team is admitted to practice in the United States District Courts for Eastern and Western Districts of Washington and Oregon as well as Washington and Oregon State Courts.

We are a debt relief agency. We help people file for bankruptcy relief under the U.S. Bankruptcy Code.
